==Transitions==

```css
img{
    /*This moves item left (negative) and right (positive) on x-axis*/
    transform: translateX();
    /*This moves item up (negative) and down (positive) on y-axis*/
    transform: translateY();
    /*This moves item on x and y axes*/
    transform: translate(x,y);   
    
    /*becomes larger or smaller based on X-times size...you can also do sizing through x and y axes too*/
    transform: scale();
    
    /*becomes rotates based on xdeg - (90deg)...you can also rotate through x and y axes too*/
    transform: rotate();
    
    /*TIPS: If you add rotate and translate together the center of rotation is located from the starting point*/
}
```

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oYlJR4Le228&list=PL4cUxeGkcC9iGYgmEd2dm3zAKzyCGDtM5&index=3

```css
.circle {
    background:white;
    /*transition -> transformation length timing*/
    transition: 1s;
    OR
    /*can add length timing per changed element like so...*/
    transition: background 1s, transform 0.3s;
    OR
    /*can add a delay time after length timing*/
    transition: background 1s, transform 0.3s 1s:
    OR 
   /*can add how the length timing is eased in*/
    transition: background 1s, transform 0.3 1s ease;
}
.circle:hover {
    background: pink;
    /*transform added features*/
    transform:rotate(360deg);
}
```

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PjR97QzOrJM&list=PL4cUxeGkcC9iGYgmEd2dm3zAKzyCGDtM5&index=4

==KeyFrames==

```css
.item {
    position:absolute;
    top:0;
    left:0;
    animation-name: animationName;
    animation-duration:3s;
}
@keyframes animationName {
    from{transform: translateX(0)}
    to{ transform: translateX(500px)}
}
```

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=irJXZnA3g5U&list=PL4cUxeGkcC9iGYgmEd2dm3zAKzyCGDtM5&index=5

```css
.item {
    position:absolute;
    top:0;
    left:0;
    animation-name: animationName;
    animation-duration:3s;
    /*creates item to stay at end of animation frame*/
    animation-fill-mode:forwards;
}
@keyframes animationName {
    from{transform: translateX(0)}
    to{ transform: translateX(500px)}
}
```

